Fully managed database proxy for RDS
Allows apps to pool and share DB connections established with the database
Improve database efficiency by reducing the stress on database resources and minimizing open connections
Serverless, autoscaling, highly available (multi az)
Reduced RDS & Aurora failover time by up to 66%
Supports RDS and Aurora
  MySQL
  PostgresSQL
  MariaDB
  MS SQL Server
No Code changes are required for most apps
Enforce IAM authentication for DB and securely store credentials in AWS Secrets manager
RDS Proxy is never publicly assessable.  Must be accessed from VPC

Lambda is majorly helped with the RDS Proxy
